{"type": "article", "id": 9503, "title": "这个设计了不起之今日最佳", "description": "我们尝试推荐一些最近发现的聪明设计。好设计并不只是一种装饰，它还是人们对于生活细节的各种思考。", "date": "2015-05-13T07:58:57Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 3149, "name": "灯具"}, {"id": 3786, "name": "包袋"}, {"id": 3281, "name": "铅笔"}, {"id": 5632, "name": "躺椅"}, {"id": 10043, "name": "痴呆症"}, {"id": 10044, "name": "Rodd"}, {"id": 10045, "name": "Filson"}], "category": 17, "author": 49585, "comment_count": 8, "praise_count": 61, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021022583aZO8MVzSDe6wQuB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>\r\n\tOde by Rodd\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t痴呆症往往会为患者带来营养不良的问题，英国的一份报告显示，45% 的痴呆症患者会出现明显的体重下降的情况，50% 的患者无法保证日常所需的进食量。于是英国设计公司 Rodd 推出了这款叫做 “Ode” 的设备。这款设备在一日三餐的进餐时间自动散发饭菜的香味，提醒痴呆症患者用餐，来保证其健康。同时，使用者可以根据饮食习惯选择不同的味道，避免出现素食主义者的房间肉味萦绕的情况。<a href=\"http://www.myode.org/\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以查看具体信息。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102238EfFDSWqoHh4p3VXK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60306122\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102238Hbct63UBq2idYkgI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.60306122\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022398wqpDeWId6VRmJtL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102239psxHc5OqCzk2jK4W.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70224719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102240l2BfkagUeX6omtGq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.70224719\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102240SrvIs93BXtbNDplE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tLeano by Nik Lorbeg\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t“Leano” 的名字听起来就好像在让你停下来，靠在路边休息一会儿。它是一个小毯子，又是一个小躺椅，它可以卷起来随身携带，平铺在地面上便可以让你随时随地休息，对于湖边休息，草地野餐，看星星看月亮，都是个不错的选择，支撑体采用的是实心榉木，而毯子采用的是耐磨的织物。这款作品有黄色，藏青色，绿色三种颜色可选，目前正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/nikcanfly/leano-have-a-chair-everywhere\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以支持他们。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022410xJhHoCelbNjXnz8.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102243Pj2hr8v9dzV7pq1Z.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56176471\" data-format=\"gif\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102246ZJ5dqjaf3p8GTxrn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61124694\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102247DMLiNEJO8gXfGd1Q.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.50488998\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102247kR4ZxMqNVc3szmin.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.38508557\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102247lY4N70SbPAkniarO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.5207824\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102248ovhN8P7mQlrcpnOD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.09168704\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022480CyQ9TvZHoswWIqz.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.94987775\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102249yNwkI6piWfxnQvE0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.1002445\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tPenxo by Brian Ton Tak\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t这是一款没有弹簧，按键等任何机械零件的铅笔，利用古老的重力学控制铅芯的进出。设计师 Brian Ton Tak 试图去除掉铅笔里面复杂的零件，保留最重要的部分。同时，设计师要求它满足可持续发展的需求。因此，这款铅笔使用的材料是航空级的铝 6061-T651 ，材质轻盈并且可以回收使用。目前铅笔外壳有黑色，银色和金色三种颜色可选，售价 35 美元，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/bitsfactory/penxo-the-most-minimalistic-2mm-lead-holder-pencil\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里</a>可以购买。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102249qY6AClDZOevb95aH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.65036675\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102250aq9MisI5btYl4cdp.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.40342298\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022504pvYBdQfzoxhGg9J.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87163814\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102251NP6DZHVfOUjYTxgJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.89242054\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022516XukNoiaT2ESlMIe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66625917\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102251scDheYqKx6GwdFHA.jpg\" alt=\"\" style=\"width:601px;white-space:normal;\" data-ratio=\"0.93857143\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102252gRId64bStjT9Wh1V.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.00428571\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102252OwWE3M0RQI6CPjxX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48899756\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tGreen by Filson \r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t美国户外品牌 Filson 发布了一个名为 “Green” 的防水包袋系列，整体以军绿色为主色调，包含有不同尺寸的背包，旅行包等六个款式，材料上采用的是聚酯纤维，上面有乙烯基涂层，防水耐用。不管在什么环境下，这款包包都是防水的给力帮手。这个系列价格在 35 美元到 200 美元之间，<a href=\"http://www.filson.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是购买链接</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022521iY2VphDUE6qc5mX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.57407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102253tCl8Z29yBgF5sVed.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.13839286\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102253piHNBly0rUdQYPOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51388889\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102254avO6UKD9bAVWmwkM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.77592593\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102254BkWOCaZ4eJDxEGqf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.87962963\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<h2>\r\n\tDual Land - Chapter I by Faberhama\r\n</h2>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t来自荷兰阿姆斯特丹的设计工作室 Faberhama 由 Paola Amabile 和 Alberto Fabbian 两位设计师创办，他们始终坚持在传统中进行现代化的创新。这个叫做 “Dual Land” 的系列灯具灵感来自远古的荷兰须德海和威尼斯的海洋文化，在过去，金属框架玻璃灯担任着海上照明的重任。他们把传统的玻璃吹制与 3D 打印相结合，试图唤起人们对遗忘的物体的回忆。<a href=\"http://www.faberhama.com/\" target=\"_blank\">这是工作室的主页</a>，感兴趣的话可以查看他们更多作品。\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin-top:0px;margin-bottom:0px;font-size:11px;line-height:normal;font-family:Helvetica;min-height:13px;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102254dxO3VsmznFqp5tjC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.734375\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102255JW3KPrtUjBanhC9z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022558QI7Lx13PH2KhVcM.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.08958333\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201607021022564K0auhs6BVE5nJXf.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102256a9kTe32PE4DQ50z7.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102257PqFOs3NaG6IZv8xL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102257bUSpmBrzZE7klsyg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.515625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702102257ZkHcowThL0pVnfuR.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6875\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}